# Xiao.2021.endothelial.immunometabolism

<!-- badges: start -->
<!-- badges: end -->

This package contains the liquid chromatography-mass spectrometry data associated
with the publication:

> Xiao W, Oldham WM, Priolo C, Pandey AK, Loscalzo J. Immunometabolic Phenotypes: 
Integrative Molecular Mechanisms Linking Inflammation and Glucose Metabolism in 
the Endothelium. 2021.
